snippet.textDisplay: For some reason, this made me feel oddly sad and inspired, nostalgic and hopeful. I really felt like I was there, helping a friend through their journey and I’m surprised at how Ashley can take us on the ride and make such a touching and heart-warming video. I think it’s also because I’m graduating high school soon and planing on moving out-of-state that these types of videos where Ashley is very reflective make me feel not so alone and like I have an older sister figure or a really good friend to experience the shifts of life together with. If you’re reading this Ashley please know I love you and your videos. They mean a lot to me and I hope you know that all of the hard work you put into them - we notice it and appreciate it so much and we’re very grateful for it. Oh but also, please take care of yourself and if you can, try to not worry about all the small details because we will love your videos all the same ! Good luck with the move and everything! ♡
